{"tid":713503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想問賭波輸晒啲錢仲通街差人錢唔跳樓可以點","createTime":"2018-06-23T00:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T10:50:21.000Z","uid":161086,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"55952c1f043e24502bbaeb617a9170f891e66979","tid":713503,"uid":161086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T00:22:26.000Z","msg":"已經冇晒錢 好後悔學左賭"},{"pid":"b049407060abd301be92d94b3dbbe9eb90edc943","tid":713503,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T00:25:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"980098fbf1681620eea2b5207a3883803f353788","tid":713503,"uid":86684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T00:26:06.000Z","msg":"收手啦，仲後生。<br />\n我兄弟差人40個都係做地盤慢慢還清，依家講唔上有錢，但最起碼三餐都夠食，草到錢"},{"pid":"7b14ab92ffb15b0672418cf62eb11f786f8773c2","tid":713503,"uid":126534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T00:26:49.000Z","msg":"生命可貴，三思"},{"pid":"a8605bc4bb530d8c3a5033621516d73b3eab9a92","tid":713503,"uid":122513,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:02:21.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=QtpeFnbj0S7RMojtUuuwcjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=b2381a58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>？那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『真心話室』（星期一至日，下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！"},{"pid":"d83b23e2e8d15cb89afae7406b556bba1a22bae7","tid":713503,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:45:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae00a46467cee1ea6f185db78c57a122286d4549","tid":713503,"uid":116364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:48:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0bf4661db4d8086accde6436471f1e05132c961","tid":713503,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:49:37.000Z","msg":"追"},{"pid":"2b2e18222824114cfcd66504dd11fb88ad95727d","tid":713503,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55952c1f043e24502bbaeb617a9170f891e66979","tid":713503,"uid":161086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T00:22:26.000Z","msg":"已經冇晒錢 好後悔學左賭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:51:08.000Z","msg":"有冇睇杜汶澤最近係Viu 嗰套乜乜去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872c5a64e1d85c948ea49b08a02cff127da7e485","tid":713503,"uid":45487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:59:59.000Z","msg":"返大陸台灣囉<br />\n但前提係唔好搞到屋企人"},{"pid":"4b4a247bf5f73104bff5cc152cfe269f6973e091","tid":713503,"uid":53421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"廢人"},{"pid":"a400f243b178ade7eb8340a2de6b8bff3183e0e7","tid":713503,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:12:19.000Z","msg":"咪撚賭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df80bae5e10b9a84cd426ed2659151eff2a67c25","tid":713503,"uid":63774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"打劫銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe8749979a38576273994b286f1662934f6f96c","tid":713503,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:45:18.000Z","msg":"咩叫學左賭？你真係學左賭跟個麥春lulu揾食而家睇緊樓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a1fef3c9bd409bd12d897cd3d4974b41551879","tid":713503,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:50:21.000Z","msg":"返大陸"}]}